
    VIM - Windows
===============================
    ctrl+w v    Opens current buffer in vertical window 
    ctrl+w s    Opens current buffer in horizontal window


    ctrl+w {h,j,k,l}    Move between open windows
    ctrl+w {H,J,K,L}    Move window around

    ... possible to use tabs
    
    ctrl+w T            Move current buffer to new window in new tab

